paragraphs.text:
run(sql="
    select orderDate, ftus/total_orders* 100 as ftu_percent from(
    select ao.orderDate, count(distinct ao.subOrderId) as total_orders,count(distinct f.orderId) as ftus from `temp.attributed_Orders` ao left join `temp.FTUs` f on ao.orderId=f.orderId
    where DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE(),ao.orderDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 30
    and 
        (lower(ao.utmContent) like '%never%'
                AND lower(ao.utmContent) like '%beta%'
                AND lower(ao.utmContent) like '%app%'
                AND lower(ao.utmContent) like '%roas%')
    and ao.Channel='FB Channel'
    group by ao.orderDate order by ao.orderDate)
",1000)
